Join our upcoming batch DIPLOMA IN MAKEUP Artistry starts from june 9th onwards , includes hair makeup and saree draping 

80days course , includes 40 days internship and 40 days training 

This course is specially designed and curated by Priyanka Harish, if u are beginner , don’t have knowledge about the basics don’t worry we shall help u 

Course includes 
* Basic to advance of Makeup , u will learn all the futuristic skills of makeup from Priyanka Harish includes 8 demonstrations, SFX makeup , groom makeup , Matured skin makeup 
* Complete theoretical knowledge with all advanced skills required to ace the world of beauty 
* Basic to advance of hairstyles , hair-prep , curls , braids , international textures etc is part of the course 
* Add on courses like , floral art , nail art , marketing , communication , social media , studio management, client handling, lighting , photography etc is part of the course 

All the products will be given for practice , we provide only and only high - end cosmetics for practice and give u exposure of all varieties of products for practice to improve your skills and product knowledge 

Every enrolment gets 30k worth of goodies , one portfolio shoot and ISO with central govt certification is provided
